Challenge #1

A 3-tier environment is a common setup. Use a tool of your choosing/familiarity create these resources on a cloud environment (Azure/AWS/GCP). Please remember we will not be judged on the outcome but more focusing on the approach, style and reproducibility.

Solution:

Pre-requisites:

Azure Subscription account
Azure devOps
Storage account for storing TfState file (You can create Storage account while running the release pipeline and you can pass the Storage account values)

DevOps Tools:

GitHub, Source Code Management
Azure Devops, for Continuous Integration
Terraform for Cloud Provisioning Tool
Azure, for public cloud service platform
